<H3> <TI>   Art Troupes Arrive for Friendship Art Festival </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Art Troupes Arrive for Friendship Art Festival </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0304085194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0807 GMT 3 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0304085194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 3 (KCNA) -- An art troupe of the 
International Federation of Koreans for Reunification and a 
Kazakh art troupe arrived here Saturday to participate in the 
12th April spring friendship art festival. 
  They were met at the airport by Choe Yong-ku, vice-minister 
of Culture and Art, and other officials concerned. 
  Earlier, an art troupe of Koreans in China arrived here by 
train. 

</TEXT>

