BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA April 6 -- Documents on cooperation 
between Vietnam and Bulgaria were signed here this evening. 
  Signatories were Ngo The Dan deputy minister of agriculture 
and food industry, and head of the Vietnamese sub-commission and 
of the Vietnamese Government's economic delegation, and Rumen 
Khristov, head of the Bulgarian sub-commussion and of the 
Bulgarian Government's economic delegation. The documents 
include minutes of the 15th session of the Vietnam- Bulgaria 
Inter-Governmental Commission for Economic, Scientific and 
Technological Cooperation, a document on amendment of 
regulations on the organization of the commission, and, an 
agreement on veterinary hygiene between Vietnam and Bulgaria. 

