nuclear forward base, military information-gathering centre and 
to lead the situation of the Korean peninsula to the grave brink 
of war. 
  The Federation of South Koreans in Japan for Democracy and 
Unification in a statement strongly urged the United States to 
withdraw at once the projected Patriots deployment in South 
Korea and stop all kinds of war games including the provocative 
"Team Spirit" joint military exercises. 

