group of human dregs and hooligans who are clean indifferent to 
the desire of the nation and the trend of the times. 
  The Kim Yong-sam group is trying to find a way out in 
bringing anti-reunification storm, following outside forces. 
But it is a foolish dream. 
  The Kim Yong-sam group must stop anti-reunification 
suppression at once. 

