<F P=102>   SK0704112194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1048 GMT 7 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0704112194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 7 (KCNA) -- Pedro Margolles 
Villanueva, director general of the PRENSA LATINA of Cuba, and 
his entourage arrived here today. 
  The guests were met at the airport by Kim Ki-yong, director 
general of the KOREAN CENTRAL NEWS AGENCY, and Jose Ramon 
Rodriguez Varona, Cuban ambassador to Korea. 

</TEXT>

