BFN 

  [Text] A regiment of the invading troops of the communist 
Vietnamese puppets and the two-headed government -- backed by 
five tanks, artillery, and multiple rocket batteries -- launched 
an attack on 5 April to break through our forces surrounding 
them in Sala Krau. The enemy was completely routed. Here is 
the preliminary result: We killed 15 soldiers and wounded a 
large number. Furthermore, we smashed and killed nine division 
and regimental officers, including a deputy to Prum Moranak, a 
tank commander, and three infantry commanders. We seized some 
weapons and war materiel. 

