  [Text] Pyongyang, April 8 (KCNA) -- His Majesty King 
Norodom Sihanouk of Cambodia, who had been paying an official 
goodwill visit to Korea upon the invitation of President Kim 
Il-song of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, left 
Pyongyang today by special plane, concluding his successful 
visit. 
