  [Text] Pyongyang, April 8 (KCNA) -- The Seventh Session of 
the Ninth Supreme People's Assembly [SPA] of the Democratic 
People's Republic of Korea which opened here April 6 closed 
today after successfully discussing the items on the agenda. 
  The session adopted with the unanimous approval of the 
deputies the decision of the SPA "on the review of the 
performance of the state budget of the DPRK for 1993" and the 
ordinance of the SPA "on the state budget of the DPRK for 1994." 

