<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Article Dedicated to Kim Chong-il Work </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Article Dedicated to Kim Chong-il Work </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0404233194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1507 GMT 4 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0404233194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 4 (KCNA) -- The dear leader Comrade 
Kim Chong-il, in his historical work "On Some Questions in 
Understanding the Chuche Philosophy" published on April 2, 1974, 
gave a comprehensive exposition of the basic characteristics of 
the chuche philosophy, the chuche-based viewpoint of man, the 
chuche-based outlook on the world, a scientific understanding of 
independence and other theoretical and practical questions 
arising in the development of the chuche philosophy. 
  In a by-lined article dedicated to the 20th anniversary of 
the publication of the work, NODONG SINMUN today says it is a 
monumental work that newly formulates all the fundamentals of 
the chuche philosophy and systematizes them in an integral whole 
and an immortal famous work greatly conducive to the development 
of the philosophical idea of the working class. 
  It says: 
  The dear leader expounds that the chuche philosophy is an 
anthropocentric philosophy which is elaborated and systematized, 
focussing on man. This is a scientific formulation of the basic 
characteristics and originality of the chuche philosophy. 
  The chuche philosophy is fundamentally different from the 
human philosophy. It does not explain the human question only 
but raises such fundamental questions as the relationship 
between the world and man and the position and role of man in 
the world and elucidates the man-centred outlook on the world. 
  The work is a precious ideological and theoretical treasure 
which newly raises and explains the human question and a great 
textbook of the chuche idea which gives a new correct outlook of 
the chuche philosophy on the world. 
  The dear leader defined man as a social being with 
independence, creativity and consciousness, thus making it clear 
that the chuche philosophy and the bourgeois human philosophy 
are diametrically opposed to each other in their view of man. 
  By elucidating the view of the world that nature and society 
are dominated and transformed by man, the chuche philosophy 
brilliantly fulfilled the philosophical task of our time in 
which the popular masses are masters of their own destiny and 
history. 
  It is a noteworthy event in the history of human philosophy 
that the dear leader gave a scientific exposition of the 
formation and development of man's independence and its 
characteristics. 
  The chuche philosophy explains that independence is not a 
product of evolution but a social product. As a result, it has 
been made clear that man is not a simple biological being that 
represents on the highest level such natural attribute as desire 
for existence which other living matter in general has, but the 
most developed social being that represents such social 
attribute as independence which other living matter cannot have. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS4-5176 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas068_c_94025" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-068 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  8 Apr 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Meeting Marks 1974 Kim Chong-il Health Care Work </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Meeting Marks 1974 Kim Chong-il Health Care Work </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0804060494 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0516 GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0804060494 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 8 (KCNA) -- A national meeting 
marking the 20th anniversary of the publication of "On Further 
Developing Health Care for the People", a work of the dear 
leader Comrade Kim Chong-il, on April 9, 1974 was held here 
Thursday. 
  The dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il in the work expounded 
on 
a scientific basis upon the essence, character and main duty of 
socialist medicine which meets the demand of the chuche idea, 
stressing that hygienic propaganda, hygienic culture and 
hygienic and preventive work must be energetically conducted for 
the implementation of the party's policy of prophylactic 
medicine. 
  Saying medical service for the people is not a mere 
technical 
work but an important political work, he elucidated detailed 
questions arising in the development of health care such as 
waging a vigorous movement for kind service, widely introducing 
Koryo therapy, consolidating the material and technical 
foundations of hopitals and improving health care by upgrading 
the level of specialization. 
  Vice-Premier of the Administration Council Chang Chol 
delivered a report at the meeting. 
  He said the work of the dear leader serves as a highly 
important guideline for developing health service in conformity 
with the demand of the developing revolution when the modelling 
of the whole society on the chuche idea has surfaced to the fore 
and thus defending and exalting the health care system of 
anthropocentric Korean-style socialism and is an immortal 
classic work that gives flawless answers to all theoretical and 
practical questions arising in the ultimate solution of the 
health care problem. 
  Reviewing the achievements registered in health service over 
the past 20 years since the publication of the work, he stated 
the people's right to medical treatment is ensured on a high 
level as the people enjoy ever greater benefits of the 
communistic health care policy of the Workers' Party of Korea 
[WPK]. 
  The meeting was attended by secretary of the WPK Central 
Committee Kim Chung-nin, officials concerned and health workers. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

