<H3> <TI>   Economic Agreements Signed With Vietnam </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Economic Agreements Signed With Vietnam </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0804013794 Hanoi VNA in English 1425 GMT 7 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK0804013794 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA April 7 -- Documents on economic, 
cultural and scientific and technological cooperation between 
Vietnam and Laos was signed in Vientiane this morning. 
  These documents include an agreement on economic, cultural, 
scientific and technological cooperation for 1994 between the 
Vietnamese and Lao Government, an agreement on general mechanism 
of economic, cultural, scientific and technological cooperation 
between the two governments and an agreement relating to sending 
and receiving Vietnamese experts to work in Laos. 
  The signing took place at the end of the 16th session of the 
Vietnam-Laos intergovernmental commission on economic, cultural, 
scientific and technological cooperation opened in Vientiane on 
April 4. 
  During its stay in Laos, the Vietnamese delegation to the 
meeting headed by Vice Prime Minister Phan Van Khai visited 
Luang Prabang Province. This afternoon the Vietnamese 
delegation left Vientiane for home. 

</TEXT>

