  [Text] Hanoi VNA April 7 -- Deputy Foreign Minister Vu 
Khoan is leading a Vietnamese delegation to the annual meeting 
of the Economic and Social Commission for Asia and the Pacific 
(ESCAP) being held in New Delhi India. 
